 "textcontent_ej7ntpzhd5l_html": "We not only make the country\u2019s finest red meat, but through sustainable job creation, we empower our farmers and butchers to build a brighter future. Our strategy is to focus first on identifying consumer needs, then work with our farmers to grow animals and apply our expertise to meet those needs.",
