 "headingtext_8ze6slpbdv6_html": "A MEASURABLE IMPACT",
 "textcontent_alt95xz3row_html": "We believe business not only has the ability to be a part of environmental solutions, but also a moral responsibility to address them.We are the first carbon neutral company in Oman. MLS has committed to the United Nations\u2019 Climate Neutral Now initiative \u2013 estimating, reducing and compensating its greenhouse gas emissions in an effort to make no net release into the atmosphere."
